      h2 Access To Initialized Instance
      p If you use automatic initalization to init Swiper (with <code>init:true</code> prop) and need to use its <a href="../docs/swiper.html">Methods and Properties</a> you can access its initialized instance by accessing <code><b>.swiper</b></code> component's property.